1) Caching declaration
2) Caching configuration -> specify ehCache config details in ehcache.xml, which contains info related to diskStorage location of cacheData 	and memory allocated to cache.
 
3) Enable caching




http://javabeat.net/spring-cache/


Finally, caching HttpClient includes support the Cache-Control extensions specified by RFC 5861.
We believe HttpClient Cache is unconditionally compliant with RFC-2616.

